226
00:09:51,489 --> 00:09:54,149
But this may be written like a metaphor.

227
00:09:54,149 --> 00:09:56,456
Because often in writing and communication,

228
00:09:56,456 --> 00:09:58,782
metaphors are used in this way.

229
00:09:58,782 --> 00:10:02,895
